        "title": "fix(agent-os): harden full-local substrate",
        "body": "﻿Summary\n- Hardens the Agent OS full-local Docker substrate: loopback publish defaults, full publish override handling, isolated Blackboard DB, package inclusion, and live proof paths.\n- Makes ticket/proof contracts more explicit, preserves capability-profile custom skills, and keeps memory-wiki full-local calls above the Gateway timeout.\n- Tightens Sentinel/sidecar security: ephemeral default vault/state, fingerprinted validator state, atomic Blackboard status migration, FTS rebuild, and safer legacy vault migration.\n\nVerification\n- node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.full-core-support-boundary.config.ts test/scripts/full-local-docker.test.ts\n- node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/agent-os-contracts.test.ts\n- node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.tooling.config.ts test/scripts/capability-agent-profile.test.ts\n- node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs extensions/memory-wiki/src/cli.ts scripts/agents/capability-agent-profile.mjs scripts/docker/full-local.mjs scripts/docker/sidecars/blackboard-cli.cjs scripts/docker/sidecars/nvidia-key-validator.cjs scripts/docker/sidecars/signal-hub.cjs scripts/docker/sidecars/windows-node.cjs scripts/lib/agent-os-contracts.cjs test/scripts/agent-os-contracts.test.ts test/scripts/capability-agent-profile.test.ts test/scripts/full-local-docker.test.ts\n- node_modules/.bin/oxfmt.cmd --check --threads=1 changed files\n- docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.sidecars.yml config --quiet\n- npm pack --dry-run --json --ignore-scripts, required files present\n- pnpm docs:list\n- literal NVIDIA key scan across branch diff: none\n- python .agents\\skills\\autoreview\\scripts\\autoreview --mode local --codex-bin node_modules\\.bin\\codex.cmd, clean\n- node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs proof\n- node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs smoke\n- node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs golden\n\nBehavior addressed: Full-local can boot a local Agent OS substrate, route a Blackboard ticket, record proof, restart signal-hub, and preserve ticket/proof evidence while keeping powerful control ports loopback by default.\nReal environment tested: Windows host with Docker Desktop, rebuilt openclaw:local image, full-local Docker compose stack, local Node/Vitest tooling.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: Rebuilt with `node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs up`, then ran `node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs proof`, `node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs smoke`, and `node scripts/docker/full-local.mjs golden`.\nEvidence after fix: Final smoke ticket `94b5aa3c-0d3b-444e-b0c9-4d0265a90c82` completed with status DONE; final golden ticket `23144982-7181-4316-b7b6-8f591711c5b0` had no failed checks.\nObserved result after fix: Gateway, Sentinel, signal-hub, and obsidian-syncer were healthy; Gateway/Sentinel readyz passed; memory-wiki status passed; golden checks confirmed ticket accepted, routed, completed, proof events listed, contract checks passed, signal-hub restarted, Blackboard ready after restart, ticket survived restart, and proof survived restart.\nWhat was not tested: Broad Testbox/Crabbox changed gates were not run because the local Crabbox/Testbox tooling was unavailable in this worktree; the proof above used local Docker Desktop instead.\n\nSupersedes closed PR #88746.\r\n",
